<section
  id="about"
  class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6 bg-navy-light relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Subtle Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(#d4af37_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:40px_40px]"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
      <!-- Image Column -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-4 border border-gold/20 rounded-2xl -z-10 translate-x-4 translate-y-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="/images/oficina.jpg"
            alt="Oficina Legal Berlan Paniagua"
            width="800"
            height="1000"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy/20 group-hover:bg-navy/0 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Experience Badge -->
        <div
          class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-6 md:-right-10 bg-gold p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl animate-float"
        >
          <div class="text-navy text-center">
            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold font-serif mb-1">12+</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold"
              >Años de<br />Experiencia</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content Column -->
      <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0">
        <span
          class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-6 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.3em] text-gold uppercase border border-gold/30 rounded-full"
        >
          Perfil Profesional
        </span>
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-white leading-tight"
        >
          Berlan <span class="text-gold italic font-serif">Paniagua</span>
        </h2>

        <div
          class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg italic font-light"
        >
          <p>
            Con una trayectoria sólida y un compromiso inquebrantable, me
            especializo en brindar
            <span class="text-white font-medium"
              >soluciones legales integrales</span
            > que protegen los intereses de mis clientes.
          </p>
          <p>
            Mi enfoque combina la <span
              class="text-gold underline decoration-gold/30 underline-offset-8"
              >experiencia técnica</span
            > con un trato humano, asegurando que cada caso reciba la atención meticulosa
            que merece.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Expertise Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12">
          {
            [
              {
                title: "Derecho Notarial",
                icon: "M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z",
              },
              {
